        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Valentine’s Day is more than a date on the calendar — it’s a celebration of togetherness, affection, and the beautiful bond you share with your wife. It’s the perfect occasion to express what words often can’t — your gratitude, admiration, and love.</p><p>If you’re searching for the perfect <strong>valentine day gift for wife</strong>, nothing compares to fine jewelry. It’s timeless, meaningful, and designed to make her feel as special as she truly is. Whether you’re newly married or have spent decades together, a diamond crafted with love is a gift she’ll treasure for years to come.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Personalised Jewelry: A Gift as Unique as She Is",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Personalised Jewelry: A Gift as Unique as She Is</h2>",
            "custom_id": "22carat"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gEUkmH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_is_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Personalisation makes a beautiful piece of jewelry even more special. Engraved rings, name pendants, or initials on a bracelet transform a simple ornament into a memory you both cherish.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
