        "rich_text_ctijNA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. The Charm of Rose Gold",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. The Charm of Rose Gold</h3><p>Warm, elegant, and feminine — rose gold embodies tenderness. A<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> makes for an exceptional <strong>valentine day special gift for wife</strong>, blending contemporary style with timeless grace. It complements both ethnic and western looks, making it a versatile piece she’ll adore.</p><h3>2. Celebrate Her Strength with a Cocktail Ring</h3><p>For the woman who lights up every room with her confidence, a bold<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/cocktail-rings-diamond\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cocktail rings diamond</span></a> piece is the perfect choice. Its brilliance symbolizes her vibrant energy and individuality. A statement ring not only elevates her style but also reflects the strong, beautiful woman she is.</p><h3>3. Matching Couple Rings: Together, Always</h3><p>Few things are as romantic as wearing matching bands that signify your eternal bond.<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Couple rings</span></a> from Lucira capture your unity and make for a sentimental <strong>Valentine’s Day best gift for wife</strong>. Each design tells a story of two souls intertwined by love and promise.</p>",
            "custom_id": "importance"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Symbolic Jewelry with Deeper Meaning",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Symbolic Jewelry with Deeper Meaning</h2>",
            "custom_id": "check"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XJgEXF": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Check_a_22_Carat_Gold_Hallmark_3e978921-1d2a-477d-b793-79806196b217.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Jewelry often carries emotions beyond its sparkle. Choose designs that symbolize your relationship — hearts for love, infinity signs for eternity, or knots for unbreakable bonds.</p><p>A heart pendant expresses affection, an infinity bracelet stands for never-ending commitment, and a minimalist diamond band represents everlasting loyalty. Symbolic jewelry adds layers of sentiment, making your gift more than just precious metal and stones — it becomes an emblem of your journey together.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
