        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Make This Valentine’s Day Unforgettable",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Make This Valentine’s Day Unforgettable</h2><p>Valentine’s Day is about celebrating love that lasts. This year, go beyond ordinary gifts. Choose jewelry that tells her story — your story — with elegance, meaning, and sparkle.</p><p>Explore <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira’s</span></a> Valentine Collection today and discover timeless designs that say “I love you” in the most unforgettable way. Because the best <strong>valentine day gift for wife</strong> is one that shines forever.</p>",
